# compose spec platform agnostic

+docker +podman +compose +stack +k8s +kubernetes +kind


Here is a platform agnostic compose specifiction use, among other tools,
by Podman. This spec works just fine with Helm charts and Kubernetes yaml
what makes it really portable and user-friendly.

Here is the spec:
https://github.com/compose-spec/compose-spec/blob/master/spec.md

And here is the website of the compose specifiction:
https://compose-spec.io/
